Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the development of a tool for Part of Speech Tagging for code-mixed Indian social media text. 
- cs.LG (Learning) is also likely as the paper mentions the use of a Trigram Hidden Markov Model to enhance observation probabilities. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possibility as the paper deals with processing and analyzing social media text. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possibility as the paper discusses the development of a tool that utilizes various features to enhance the accuracy of Part of Speech Tagging. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is less likely but still a possibility as the paper may have used some neural network techniques in developing the tool.
